We're all just zebras, under the same African weather.
Let's break down these barriers, let's heal these old scars,
Together as one, under the same stars.

[Outro]
斑马，斑马，不再分彼此，黑与白，共舞在草原上
放下仇恨，共享生命之歌，斑马，斑马，自由自在

(Note: The rap section is designed to capture the hardcore rap style with a Linkin Park influence, while the rest of the song maintains a narrative flow with choruses and bridges to emphasize the message of unity and the futility of manufactured divisions.)





